### Project setup for Frontend
- use Material-UI for all UI comonents
- use React 18 for all UI 
- there is a folder structure ui/ each folder should be used appropriately
-- Components - should contain re-usable components
-- Main - should contain React core components
-- Pages - should contain Page entrypoints, those included in routing
-- Services - should contain any code talking to external databases or APIs
-- Utilities - re-usable and shared utilities in the project


### nvm and npm
This project has npm installed via nvm
use need to use 'nvm use v20' prior to any npm commands to make sure to get the latest and correct version